    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it a legal offence for a parent to be absent from their child's life. ",
        "additional_details": "We believe that a parent walking away from their parental responsibilities should be a legal offence. ",
        "background": "We believe that parents should not be able to choose to be absent from the life of their child without clear and enforced legal consequences. I think that usually mothers, but sometimes fathers, can be left to raise the child on their own.",
